room_title: Escape room "Summer School Breakout" by Vector Escape Games in Redlands
room_address: 1765 Orange Tree Lane Unit B Redlands CA 92374
room_description: It's your junior year of high school and its finals week! Instead of studying like the great students you are, you and your friends are going to break into the teachers office and steal the test answers instead! Can you find the answers and get out before the teacher comes back?
